        <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>name</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The name of the class</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
The constructor initializes the member variables retryCnt and retryTmoCur with 0, maxRetries with 5, retryTmoInit wirh 10 and retryTmoMax with 60. It allocate and register a mailbox and allocates and initialize the timer for delay reboot and download retry interval with a duration of 3 ms. Finally it allocates and initialize a state machine instance of class <ref refid="class_fw_fsm" kindref="compound">FwFsm</ref> to control the update process. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
