        <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para>The function defines the JSON string with an error code, an error description and a timestamp, request a message from message pool, set message type to eFwReject, set eFwUpdCtrl as sender, copy the JSON string in the message payload, retrieve a pointer to the mailbox of the MQTT connector task and send message to MQTT connector task&apos;s mailbox. </para>
